Dead tree is a scenery object found in West Ardougne during the insurrection battle in Song of the Elves. The dead tree is identical to and takes the place of the dead trees found in West Ardougne, but cannot be chopped down and has no interaction options. This is likely to prevent the player from misclicking on the tree during the fight against the mourners.

The tree was later repurposed for use in the Last Man Standing Deserted Island map.

'''Dead tree''' is a scenery object found in [[West Ardougne]] during the insurrection battle in [[Song of the Elves]]. The dead tree is identical to and takes the place of the [[dead tree]]s found in West Ardougne, but cannot be chopped down and has no interaction options. This is likely to prevent the player from misclicking on the tree during the fight against the [[mourner]]s.

The tree was later repurposed for use in the [[Last Man Standing]] Deserted Island map.
